{"tid":765991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瀋陽發生疑似非洲豬瘟疫 大量病豬被焚燒 疫區已被封鎖","createTime":"2018-08-03T08:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T03:06:19.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d998fb6671eb960d030d9bad623c5418269ae296","tid":765991,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:38:40.000Z","msg":"瀋陽發生疑似非洲豬瘟疫情疫區已被封鎖<br />\n2018年08月03日15:11 新京報<br />\n<br />\n8月2日，遼寧瀋陽沈北新區五五社區一養殖戶，經中國動物衛生與流行病學中心檢測，發生疑似非洲豬瘟疫情，根據貼出的通報顯示，目前當地已經啟動重大疫情應急預案二級響應，對疫區進行封鎖。 對所有病死豬，被撲殺豬及產品進行無害化處理。 目前各項工作穩步推進。<br />\n<br />\n另據遼沈晚報：<br />\n<br />\n8月2日下午17時，經中國動物衛生與流行病學中心診斷，我省瀋陽市沈北新區沈北街道（新城子）五五社區發生疑似非洲豬瘟疫情，並於8月3日上午11時確診。 疫情發生後，農業農村部，遼寧省委、省政府高度重視，立即啟動重大動物（Ⅱ級）疫情響應，迅速組成專家組趕赴疫區，指導撲疫工作，劃定了疫點、疫區和受威脅區，緊急部署、指導當地嚴格落實各項根除措施。<br />\n<br />\n瀋陽市、沈北新區嚴格按照《非洲豬瘟疫情應急預案》要求，對疫點、疫區存欄生豬進行撲殺、消毒和無害化處理，對受威脅區生豬進行全面採樣監測，並全面展開流行病學調查。 截至8月3日15時，疫點內913頭生豬已經全部撲殺和無害化。 消毒工作全面展開。<br />\n<br />\n目前，各項撲疫工作進展順利，疫情得到有效控制。<br />\n<br />\n非洲豬瘟是由非洲豬瘟病毒引起的豬的一種急性、熱性、高度接觸性動物傳染病，豬主要通過接觸病毒或者污染物或被感染的蜱叮咬後而感染，潛伏期為15天，世界動物衛生組織（OIE）將其列為法定報告動物疫病，我國將其列為一類動物疫病，是重點防控的外來病。 非洲豬瘟不是人畜共患病，不感染人。 近年來，非洲豬瘟在俄羅斯和東歐國家持續流行，之前國內尚未有病例報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://translate.google.com.hk/translate?sl=zh-CN&amp;tl=zh-TW&amp;js=y&amp;prev=_t&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.cn%2Fs%2F2018-08-03%2Fdoc-ihhehtqh4376076.shtml&amp;edit-text=&amp;act=url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftranslate.google.com.hk%2Ftranslate%3Fsl%3Dzh-CN%26tl%3Dzh-TW%26js%3Dy%26prev%3D_t%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26ie%3DUTF-8%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fnews.sina.com.cn%252Fs%252F2018-08-03%252Fdoc-ihhehtqh4376076.shtml%26edit-text%3D%26act%3Durl&d=ubKrzgiQmVzJPhp33jvs0ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b8002550\" target=\"_blank\">https://translate.google.com.hk/translate?sl=zh-CN&amp;tl=zh-TW&amp;js=y&amp;prev=_t&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.cn%2Fs%2F2018-08-03%2Fdoc-ihhehtqh4376076.shtml&amp;edit-text=&amp;act=url</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9t4rHh41R4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9t4rHh41R4M&d=ubKrzgiQmVzJPhp33jvs0ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=64775180\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9t4rHh41R4M</a>"},{"pid":"2d9534d456e5800a684590842a9e1f39ccfe1436","tid":765991,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DjqXzAeVAAAZGpH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDjqXzAeVAAAZGpH.jpg&h=1c155513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DjqX1vkUUAA8RyJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDjqX1vkUUAA8RyJ.jpg&h=2b777a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DjqXzAeVAAAZGpH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDjqXzAeVAAAZGpH.jpg&h=1c155513&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdd73d61fae090e8edd2a8348aae4c8179e305d0","tid":765991,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:41:32.000Z","msg":"😩🐷"},{"pid":"1326aac19637e57dc8830ede085db8483d6a17aa","tid":765991,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:43:13.000Z","msg":"BTW, source只揾到官媒報導<br />\n係咪&quot;不感染人&quot;就you think you la"},{"pid":"39db15a08983de71e1e952fa7c2a3a55d42ee5d7","tid":765991,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"同港豬沙士一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d268d7029dd67da68c4f1dcea2651d2c0f8bb65d","tid":765991,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"非洲豬瘟不是人畜共患病<br />\n14億支那畜好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c502b82aece2cd5a818f5f004e8429801fe7b6","tid":765991,"uid":29080,"like"